variant_descriptions.KORW: Bitwise OR 16 bits masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KORB: Bitwise OR 8 bits masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KORQ: Bitwise OR 64 bits masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KORD: Bitwise OR 32 bits masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.

op.text: Performs a bitwise OR between the vector mask k2 and the vector mask k3, and writes the result into vector mask k1 (three-operand form).
